reviewText: Very good for Christmas time.  Love the dogs and their adventures.
Loved the double VHS pack for the price...I have an autistic son who likes to order the same VHS over and over, so it becomes quite costly.

This movie was good, containing good characters, but Isn't sociaty tired of the Christmas Carol Plot? It has been done MANY Times. The Flintstones, The Muppets, All Dogs go to Heaven, 101 Dalmatians, and the list goes  on..
The Story starts when Anita gets Fired by Cruella on Christmas Eve,  making the Dearly's undable to pay for the Presents for the Dogs and Each  other. Then Cruella is visited byt three ghosts (Played by  Cute-as-a-button- Cadpig, Spot the Chicken, and Rolly).. and you know the  rest.
